event.title: MSBI Online Training Demo in chennai - Intellipaat
event.description:
Intellipaat is organizing a free demo for MSBI Online Training. This demo is for the MSBI Training in chennai, is Offered By Intellipaat, in this Demo You will know the complete aspects of SSIS, SSRS, and SSAS.

What will you learn in this MSBI Course Demo in chennai ?

MSBI architecture

Data modeling, transformation, and representation

Data flow across components

Working with OLAP database and table

Deploying analytical techniques with MSBI

Multidimensional data modeling and cube creation

Creating charts, dashboards, and reports

Who can join the MSBI training course Demo event?

Software Architects, ETL Developers, and Data Analysts

Business Intelligence Professionals and people looking to upskill themselves in MSBI

Before joining the event, you should know the basics of MSBI

MSBI Tutorial
